    "title": "Really Long Books That Are Worth Every Page",
    "preview_text": "Oh man, there is nothing I love more than a big, long, thick biography. Last month, we talked about short books you could finish on a plane, well I’m talking about the opposite of that now, the ones",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFOEZSeaIAAmJEr.jpg",
