          "key": "6lc4j",
          "text": "Kids\n​I sometimes end these emails with kid recommendations. Obviously, there aren’t that many enormous biographies that kids enjoy, but my oldest is obsessed with Hamilton so we listened to the audiobook of Ron Chernow’s 832-page biography on Alexander Hamilton. He loved it so much that when I had Ron Chernow on the Daily Stoic Podcast, he made a cameo in the interview to ask his own questions about the book and the musical (you can see that here). It’s also become his gift of choice for his friends' birthday parties, which is often met with an “uhhh…thanks” from the parents.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        }
